Hello everybody! In episode 12 of my Kerbal Space Program LP I land a Kethane drilling rig on the mun!

It is a basic walk through essentially of how to set up your first Kethane drilling rig.

You can get the Kethane mod here: http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/13692-Mechanical-Mouse-Industries-Kethane-Payload-Packs-Released

Subscribe to see my next video where I attempt to transfer to Minmus from the Mun!
